(16, 30, 'Willowshire Burns!', 'The earth dragon Gorgok and his army are destroying the town of Willowshire and tower at its center! What does this terrifying new foe want from this small town?', 'The earth dragon Gorgok and his army are destroying the town of Willowshire and tower at its center! What does this terrifying new foe want from this small town?', '/quests/quest-chapter1-camp.swf', 'none', 0, 350, 0, 20000, 0, 119143, '117', 1, 25, 'Earth, Dragons, Reptiles, Sneevils', 'mset-dragonwar01.swf', '5,16,17,57', '0'),
