(35, 59, 'The VurrMen Ruins', 'These ruins once stood tall and proud, but all things change. Hunderds of years have passed and the ruins of the great city are now infested with VurrMen and Tuskmongers, drawn by the many mysterious objects that can still be found here.', 'These ruins once stood tall and proud, but all things change. Hunderds of years have passed and the ruins of the great city are now infested with VurrMen and Tuskmongers, drawn by the many mysterious objects that can still be found here.', 'random/random-ruins.swf', 'none', 0, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 5513453, '118', 1, 5, 'Rats', 'mset-oaklore.swf', '69,73,76,77', '0'),
(36, 60, 'The Ice Dragonlord', 'You have broken the army of the ice dragon. Finally, you stand face to face with Glaisaurus and his rider, the powerful Dragonlord Frostscythe!', 'The town has been freed from the icey clutches of Dragonlord Frostscythe and Glaisaurus. The evil Dragonlord is merely defeated, not destroyed. You know that you will face his power again.', 'quests/quest-icedragon-bossfight.swf', 'none', 99, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 7741, '118', 0, 0, 'none', 'none', '5,6,7', '0'),
(37, 62, 'VurrMen Tunnels', 'You have discovered the home of the VurrMen in the tunnels beneath the ruins. It appears as if they are gathering  weapons and resources. Maybe they are planning something big...', 'You have discovered the home of the VurrMen in the tunnels beneath the ruins. It appears as if they are gathering  weapons and resources. Maybe they are planning something big...', 'quests/quest-tunnel.swf', 'none', 0, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 784, '118', 1, 5, 'Rats', 'mset-oaklore.swf', '69,73,76,77', '0'),
(38, 63, 'Alls Well That Ends Well', 'You have ventured into this network of caves to stop the VurrMen from poisoning several local wells with their magic plague. ', 'With only seconds to spare you stopped the VurrMan Plaguebringer from poisoning the drinking water in this well... but there are several other wells in the area connected to the tunnels that the VurrMen have built. ', 'random/random-well.swf', 'none', 0, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 852, 'none', 1, 5, 'Rats', 'mset-oaklore.swf', '69,73,76,77', '0'),
(39, 64, 'Sir Jings Weapons', 'You find yourself at the base of mountain surrounded by storm elementals. They have gathered to use the power of Sir Jings weapons to create a never-ending storm!', 'You have fought your way up the mountain and stopped the storm elementals from summoning a never-ending storm! For the sake of the world you must take Sir Jings weapon for safe keeping. ', 'quests/quest-sirjing.swf', 'none', 4, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 6261838, 'none', 2, 5, 'Wind, Water, Energy', 'mset-storm.swf', '78,79,80,81,82,83', '0'),
(40, 65, 'Friday The 13th III, Finale!', 'It is Friday the 13th again, and the Necromantress has revealed her part in the invasion. All that remains of the war is to defeat the boss... but wait, TWO bosses??!', 'You did it! The flaming light monster Pro Pain and the Rotgut, the zombie made from the kings missing 300th warrior, have been defeated! But who have Xan and Sepulchure replaced in Falconreach?', 'quests/quest-war-Friday13Beach-BOSS.swf', 'none', 0, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 912060, 'none', 1, 99, 'Light and Dark', 'mset-friday13beachBOSS.swf', '185,186', '0'),
(41, 66, 'Night Of The Living Pumpkin', 'The town of Amityvale is located in the southern border of warm, sunny DoomWood. It is constantly under attack but the people have pretty much gotten use to it.', 'The town of Amityvale is located in the southern border of warm, sunny DoomWood. It is constantly under attack but the people have pretty much gotten use to it.', 'quests/quest-halloweenwar.swf', 'none', 17, 5000, 0, 10000, 0, 3646396, '119', 12, 29, 'Darkness, Nature', 'mset-halloween.swf', '98,97,94,93,92', '0'),
(42, 67, 'Pumpkin Pi Bomber', 'Finally the waves of monsters have finished attacking town, now you can finally see who is causing all the terror in Amityvale... and why.', 'Finally the waves of monsters have finished attacking town, now you can finally see who is causing all the terror in Amityvale... and why.', 'quests/quest-halloweenwar-boss.swf', 'none', 0, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 367324, 'none', 1, 99, 'Pumpkin', 'mset-jackboss.swf', '99,100', '0'),
