(51, 78, 'Aeris Dragon Tournament', 'Compete against fellow DragonLords in this tournament to earn a highly prized Dragon PvP Trophy!', 'Congratulations! You have won this Dragon Tournament. Below, a crowed of enthusiastic fans goes cheers for you and your dragon as fly down to receive your Dragon PvP Trophy.', 'towns/PvP/quest-pvpdragon.swf', 'none', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 77101, 'none', 0, 0, 'none', 'none', '5,6,7', '0'),
(52, 79, '100 Rooms of Fiery Doom!', 'Can you find your way through this INSANELY HUGE fire dungeon to obtain the ultra rare prize at the end?', 'Unbelievable! You have found the end of the 100 Room Dungeon of Fiery Doom!', 'random/random-100room-firecave.swf', 'none', 0, 5000, 0, 9000, 0, 1690340, 'none', 1, 99, 'Fire', 'mset-fire.swf', '42,52,115,15', '0'),
(53, 85, 'Crystal Clear Lake', 'As a favor to Thursday, you have come to the badly named Crystal Clear lake to clear a path to her herb garden.', 'You have defeated the werewolf Lon but the mystery of Thursday deepens.', 'quests/quest-lake.swf', 'none', 99, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 1824895, 'none', 1, 99, 'Water, Plant, Beast', 'mset-lake.swf', '19,128,127', '0'),
(54, 86, 'Yaga Stone Circle', 'After being handed a note by Thursday, you make your way the ancient stone circle which the Five Yaga Sisters call home to stop them from summoning the Strange Outworlder to destroy Lore.', 'You have defeated the Strange Outworlder, also known as Guffer. Who knew that a pot-bellied furball could hit so hard?', 'quests/quest-yaga2.swf', 'none', 99, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 1385846, 'none', 1, 99, 'Darkness, Nature', 'mset-yaga.swf', '131,98,130,129,97,447', '0'),
(55, 88, 'The Vampire Tower', 'It appears as if a vampire either moved into an abandoned Guardian Tower or took it over! This tower seems the be the source of most of the evil casting its shadow over Amityvale.', 'Lord Frydae XIII has fallen, but escaped at the last second in the form of a rat. No matter, you ruined his dark plans of overrunning the world with vampiric slaves. You have saved Thursday and the world!', 'quests/quest-vampirewar-boss.swf', 'none', 99, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 710021, 'none', 1, 99, 'Darkness', 'mset-vampirewar-boss.swf', '130,134,136,135,126', '0'),
(56, 96, 'Snuggle-Gram Delivery!', 'Make your way through the Forest of Infitite Terror and deliver the Snuggle-Gram to a broken hearted villager.', 'Successful Snuggle-Gram delivery! For a job well done you will earn a Token of Affection which you can turn in to Big Daddy for rare Hero Heart Day items.', 'towns/heroheart/random-herosheart.swf', 'none', 99, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 1798432, 'none', 0, 0, 'odd', 'mset-herosheart.swf', '141,142,143,145', '0'),
(57, 99, 'The Irismancer', 'You and the other heroes drove the eye monsters from town and followed their retreating trail to the Temple of the Irismancer. No doubt, it is waiting for you at the top.', 'The Irismancer was defeated but merely lost his physical form, and being a creature of its word it revealed many hidden answers to you that only it could see.', 'quests/quest-eyedefend-bossfight.swf', 'none', 99, 2000, 0, 3000, 0, 500000, 'none', 1, 99, 'Eyes', 'mset-eyes.swf', '33,147,148,149,150', '0'),
(58, 100, 'The Black Dragon Box', 'You have to find Lady Celestia before the Darkwolf bandits do, otherwise the Black Dragon Box will be lost!', 'You saved Lady Celestia and defeated the Darkwolf leader Drakath (He seemed mad about it). The Black Dragon Box was stolen by a Sneevil. Now you must head to the town of Falconreach and speak with Twilly!', 'quests/DragonEgg/quest-dragonegg1.swf', 'none', 99, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 4701957, 'none', 1, 99, 'Human', 'mset-drakath1.swf', '139,125,154', '0'),
(59, 102, 'The Worst Prank Ever', '', '', 'quests/quest-oaklore-outhouser1.swf', 'none', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 5461593, 'none', 0, 0, 'none', 'none', '5,6,7', '0'),
(60, 104, 'A Golden Opportunity', 'Robina has agreed to give you the Black Dragon Box in exchange for a few favors, the first of which is recovering a chest of gold stolen by the Darkwolf Bandits.', 'You have fought your way through the Darkwolf Bandits to their forest hideout and recovered the stolen chest for Robina. What could she want with all this gold?', 'quests/quest-robina1.swf', 'none', 5, 200, 0, 900, 0, 2716947, 'none', 1, 99, 'Human', 'mset-drakath1.swf', '139,125,154', '0'),
(61, 105, 'Give Until It Hurts', 'Robina the hood has asked you to take the gold stolen from the Darkwolf Bandits and place it on several monsters of the forest.', 'A few bites and scratches later, you have placed all of the stolen gold onto the forest monsters. Now that you have accomplished your backwards task, go see Robina for the Black Dragon Box.', 'quests/quest-robina2.swf', 'none', 0, 0, 0, 1400, 0, 2188142, 'none', 5, 10, 'beasts', 'mset-robina1.swf', '140,153,90,144', '0'),
(62, 106, 'Defeat Gananana!', 'You have assembled all four pieces of the mighty Quad-Force and now you must battle the wicked Gananana to ensure that it is never stolen again.', 'You and Robina the Hood have defeated the evil Gananana! Now the Quad-Force will be safe forever... or will it?!', 'quests/quest-eye-rule.swf', 'none', 10, 200, 0, 900, 0, 1828630, 'none', 1, 99, 'Eyes', 'mset-eyes.swf', '33,147,148,149,150', '0'),
(63, 107, 'Opening The Black Box', 'You have done everything that Robina the hood has asked and now it is time to recieve your reward... THE BLACK DRAGON BOX!', 'After opening the box and discovering that it was empty, the sneevil confessed to dumping the contents of the box at the Sneevil Dump Site. Maybe Twilly knows where that is.', 'quests/DragonEgg/quest-dragonegg2.swf', 'none', 99, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 1897157, 'none', 1, 99, 'human,beast', 'mset-drakath2.swf', '139,155', '0'),
(64, 109, 'Xan Bossfight', 'Xan is unlike any villian we have ever fought before...', 'You have stood up to Xan and are hailed the hero of Falconreach. Now, the people look onto you for inspiration as they rebuild.... Falconreach shall spread its wings again!', 'towns/WrathofXan/quest-war-wrathofxan-endingr1.swf', 'none', 99, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 1269887, 'none', 1, 99, 'fire', 'mset-xan.swf', '157', '0'),
(65, 114, 'Summoning Help', 'You have gathered all the necessary spell components that warlic needs to summon a creature from the drakness who can sniff out the real Dragon Egg!', 'You saved the Dragon Egg from being eaten by the Doomkitten, and now you know which is the real egg! Once it senses that you have found a safe place for it, it will drop its illusion and show you its true form.', 'quests/DragonEgg/quest-dragonegg7.swf', 'none', 99, 200, 0, 900, 0, 801945, 'none', 10, 15, 'Darkness and Laundry', 'mset-magetower.swf', '162,163,164,165', '0'),
(66, 115, 'Breakfast With Warlic', 'Warlic has invited you into his tower to try and help you in identify which egg is the true Dragon Egg.', 'In an attempt to save your world, you cooked the egg that you thought was the deagon egg. Luckily, you were wrong. ', 'quests/DragonEgg/quest-dragonegg5.swf', 'none', 99, 0, 0, 0, 0, 527, 'none', 0, 0, 'none', 'none', '5,6,7', '0'),
(67, 116, 'Battle Krakhim', 'Guardian Trainer Eckhard has asked that you pass his test of valor by defeating Krakhim, the strange monster brought to Surewould Forest by Drakath.', 'You defeated the beast Krakhim with ease! Return to Guardian Trainer Eckhard in Falconreach to activate your next Guardian Ability.', 'quests/quest-Guardian1.swf', 'none', 99, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 43136, 'none', 1, 99, 'human,beast', 'mset-drakath2.swf', '139,155', '0'),
(68, 117, 'A Visit To Cysero', 'Guardian Trainer Eckhard has instructed you to visit Cysero, the Mad Weaponsmith, to completely repair your armor. After several dizzying days chasing Cysero around the land you track him down in the tower that he and Warlic call home.', 'Amazing, the guardian armor that you brought to Cysero looks as good as new. Every chink , dent and scratch has vanished!', 'quests/quest-Guardian2.swf', 'none', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 25253, 'none', 0, 0, 'none', 'none', '5,6,7', '0'),
(69, 118, 'The Dread Dragonmaster', 'As you near the end of your Guardian training, Guardian Trainer Eckhard has asked you to pass the test of might by defeating Dragonmaster Frostscythe on his own turf.', 'The icy power of the dragonmaster was no match for your might. Return to Guardian Trainer Eckhard to unlock your next Guardian ability.', 'quests/quest-Guardian3.swf', 'none', 99, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 24676, 'none', 1, 99, 'ICE', 'mset-icedragon.swf', '109,108', '0'),
