(76, 134, 'Togzilla Attacks!', 'A prehistoric mutant Tog has emerged from Yokyto bay, with its army of Kaiju. You and your dragon must stop them from destroying the village! It will also be pretty good practice.', 'You have defeated Togzilla and driven it back into the sea, and the battle practice has helped your dragon develop its abilities further!', 'quests/quest-DragonTrain.swf ', 'none', 99, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 500000, 'none', 1, 99, 'Water,Energy', 'mset-togzilla.swf', '179,180,284', '0'),
(77, 136, 'Fetching Fire', 'In order to turn the river of fire back into water, Warlic needs a sample of the magical fire that is filling the river. It flows from its source deep inside a cave protected by fire.', 'You have secured a sample of the magical flaming water for Warlic. Now maybe he will be able to help the people of Lymcrest change their river back to cool, drinkable water.', 'quests/quest-Xan2-a1.swf ', 'none', 0, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 254483, 'none', 1, 99, 'fire', 'mset-lava.swf', '156,42,52,115,15', '0'),
(78, 139, 'Doomwood Destroyers', 'You must battle you way through this cursed forest to destroy the evil tree monster responsible for these corrupt trees.', 'You defeated a Doomwood Destroyer! This forest is a step closer to once again flourishing with life and purity. You have given the people of Doomwood hope!', 'random/random-trees.swf', 'none', 0, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 628320, 'none', 1, 99, 'Trees', 'mset-trees.swf', '35,91', '0'),
(79, 141, 'Castle Ruins', 'The Castle Blackskull (eleven shades darker than its gray neighbor) has been overrun by undead soldiers.  You must defeat their leader to reclaim this once glorious fortress.', 'Congratulations!  You have successfully driven the undead scourge away from the ruins of castle, Blackskull!  You have the Power!', 'towns/Doomwood/quest-CastleRuins2.swf', 'none', 9000, 10000, 0, 10000, 0, 500000, 'none', 16, 22, 'Darkness,Fire', 'mset-skeletons.swf', '101,102,103', '0'),
(80, 146, 'Osprey Cove', 'A pirates home away from home.', 'A pirates home away from home.', 'towns/ospreycove/town-ospreycove21.swf', 'none', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 197, 'ospreycove=towns/ospreycove/town-ospreycove21.swf\nweaponshop=towns/ospreycove/shop-PirateWeapon.swf\nhairshop=towns/ospreycove/shop-PirateHair.swf\npetshop=towns/ospreycove/shop-PiratePet.swf\nInn=towns/ospreycove/shop-PirateInn.swf\nInn2=towns/ospreycove/sho', 0, 0, 'none', 'none', '5,6,7', '0'),
(81, 148, 'Water Breathing Potions', 'Rhubarb in Osprey Cove has asked you to secure the hidden cargo of Water Breathing potions from the ninja invaders on the ship!', 'You saved the ship from the ninjas, only to have the whole adventure literally blow up in your face. Rhubarb had decided to save you from Captain Blackberry this time... but now you owe him!', 'towns/ospreycove/quest-pirate1.swf', 'none', 99, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 462884, 'none', 1, 99, 'Darkness,Metal', 'mset-ninja2.swf', '196,197,198', '0'),
(82, 151, 'Ruins of Kordana', 'Rhubarb has sent you to the ruins in the center of Sho Nuff Island, to try and recover the item that pirates and ninjas have been warring over for centuries... The Wind Pearl', 'Drakath is behind the theft of the wind orb instead of the ninjas! The ruins are, in reality, the remains of a giant fighting machine! Things on Sho Nuff Island are not at all what they seem.', 'towns/ospreycove/quest-pirate2r2.swf', 'none', 0, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 237571, 'none', 1, 99, 'Clockwork', 'mset-mq.swf', '112,113,201', '0'),
(83, 153, 'Attack of the Ninjas!', 'The ninjas of Sho Nuff Island are attacking Osprey Cove! Rhubarb has asked you to defend the town against the invaders while a large party of pirates attack the ninja town.', 'You have defeated this wave of ninjas, but more and more keep jumping out of the shadows to attack! How long do you think you can hold them off?', 'wars/quest-PNwar-pirate2.swf', 'none', 0, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 76519, 'none', 0, 99, 'Ninjas', 'mset-pnwar-ninjas.swf', '194,195,196,197,198', '0'),
(84, 154, 'Attack of the Pirates!', 'The pirates of Sho Nuff Island are attacking the Shadow of the Wind Village. Thyton has asked you to defend the town against the invaders while a large party of ninjas attack the pirate town.', 'You have defeated this wave of pirates, but more and more keep pouring out of the sea to attack! How long do you think you can hold them off?', 'wars/quest-PNwar-ninja.swf', 'none', 0, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 80435, 'none', 0, 99, 'Pirates', 'mset-pnwar-pirates.swf', '202,203,206,205,204', '0'),
(85, 158, 'Boxes of Ninjas', 'Rhubarb has sent you to speak to the cleverly disguised Agent 58. Inside this sneevil ninja training facility is information about Drakath. You must get it at all costs!', 'You defeated waves of crafty, not-so-deadly Elite Sneenjas and the monster called Okuchi No Okami, but does this chest hold the information that you need...?', 'towns/ospreycove/quest-pirate3.swf', 'none', 0, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 110376, 'none', 1, 99, 'Metal, Fire', 'mset-okami.swf', '210,211', '0'),
(86, 159, 'Captains Orders', 'Captain Blackberry has brought you to a cave where Drakath is hiding with the Wind Pearl. The passage is dangerous but with the Wind Pearl within reach you must risk it.', 'Whoa! It seems that Drakath activated the Wind Orb and used its power against you but it looks like he does not have control of that power yet. You HAVE to get to him before he figures out how to use that power!', 'towns/ospreycove/quest-pirate4.swf', 'none', 99, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 104697, 'none', 1, 99, 'Water', 'mset-drakath4.swf', '212,139', '0'),
(87, 160, 'Chart Captors', 'Thyton in the Shadow of the Wind Village has asked you to invade this pirate ship and steal the navigational charts from the map room.', 'Those pirates are so hurt that even their wooden peg legs will need casts! Return to Thyton and inform him of your success.', 'quests/quest-3doorsninja.swf', 'none', 0, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 489144, 'none', 1, 99, 'metal', 'mset-pnwar-pirates.swf ', '206,205,204', '0'),
(88, 163, 'Shadow of the Wind Village', 'The secret village hidden amongst the ninjas.', 'The secret village hidden amongst the ninjas.', 'towns/Ninjavillage/town-Ninjatown-pirateship.swf', 'none', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 346, 'ninjatown=towns/Ninjavillage/town-Ninjatown-pirateship.swf\nweaponshop=towns/Ninjavillage/shop-NinjaWeapon.swf\nhelmshop=towns/Ninjavillage/shop-NinjaHelm.swf\npetshop=towns/Ninjavillage/shop-NinjaPet.swf\ninn=towns/Ninjavillage/shop-NinjaInn.swf\ninn2=towns/N', 0, 0, 'none', 'none', '5,6,7', '0'),
(89, 164, 'Gorgok Returns!', 'After a healing slumber, Gorgok, the green nature dragon has awoken and plans to finish off the rest what it began! It plans to destroy all of Willowshire and every human left defending it!', 'You and your dragon have done what Guardian Fortuna and her resistance could only dream of... you defeated Gorgok! The dragon has retreated into its cave and sleeps again until it can heal. You have bought the Willowshire resistance precious time to fight', 'quests/quest-willowshiredragon2.swf', 'none', 99, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 500000, 'none', 1, 99, 'Fire?', 'mset-willowshire1.swf', '57,56,214', '0'),
(90, 166, 'The Pumpkin Kings Curse', 'The Couldron SIsters have employed you as their Part-time candy consultant which means that you need to help them in all aspects of their candy making, including defeating Jack Strife and breaking the pumpkin curse on Myx.', 'You have defeated the Pumpkin King Jack Strife and broken the curse on Myx! Return to the Cauldron Sisters and see what they need help with next!', 'zones/mogloween/quest-jackstrife.swf', 'none', 99, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 108021, 'none', 1, 99, 'Mogloween Boss', 'mset-jackstrife.swf', '99,128,132,133,100', '0'),
(91, 178, 'Walk Through Fire', 'Thyton has you hot on the trail of Drakath!', 'Whoa! It seems that Drakath activated the Wind Orb and used its power against you but it looks like he does not have control of that power yet. You HAVE to get to him before he figures out how to use that power!', 'towns/Ninjavillage/quest-ninja4.swf', 'none', 0, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 100144, 'none', 0, 99, 'Fire monsters, Drakath', 'mset-ninja4.swf', '1,20,223,139', '0'),
(92, 181, 'The Jewel of the Four Winds', 'Thyton has asked you to face Okuchi No Okami and to get the Jewel of the Four Winds from Drakath, while he gets the frightened villagers to safety.', 'YOU DID IT! You saved the Shadow of the Wind village from Okuchi No Okami, and the stolen ninja scroll skills. You are the new hero of the Shadow of the Wind ninja clan.', 'towns/Ninjavillage/quest-ninja5.swf', 'none', 0, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 115261, 'none', 1, 99, 'Okuchi and Drakath', 'mset-Okami2.swf', '139,211', '0'),
(93, 183, 'A Frostvale Tale', 'Learn the story of Frostval, and the moglins who live in the wintery village of Frostvale!', 'Learn the story of Frostval, and the moglins who live in the wintery village of Frostvale!', 'towns/frostvale/town-frostvale-book4r8.swf', 'none', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 69, 'none', 0, 0, 'none', 'none', '5,6,7', '0'),
(94, 188, 'We Three Spirits', 'The three spirits of Frostval Past, Present and Future have come to save the day.', 'With the three spirits of Frostval past Present and Future vanquished by Artix, the fate of Frostval is left to you!', 'towns/frostvale/quest-Cutscene2-07.swf ', 'none', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 97085, 'none', 0, 0, 'none', 'none', '5,6,7', '0'),
(95, 192, 'NOT USED', '', '', 'IGA/town-ballyhoo-oaklore.swf', 'none', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 288, 'none', 0, 0, 'none', 'none', '5,6,7', '0'),
(96, 193, 'Sepulchure', 'You have been asked to investigate the disturbance high in the mountains of Sho Nuff Island.', 'Who could have imagined Sepulchure and his dragon would hold such power? You narrowly escaped with your life, but at least now you have had a taste of the battles to come. How will you prepare for your next encounter?', 'quests/quest-sepulchure1.swf ', 'none', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 115763, 'none', 0, 0, 'TEST', 'mset-fluffyandseppy.swf', '228', '0'),
(97, 195, 'Run for the Oasis', 'Can you make it to the Oasis?', 'You made it!', 'quests/quest-runtooasis.swf', 'none', 0, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 500000, 'none', 9, 14, 'Elemental,Reptile,Bug', 'mset-pyramid.swf', '47,51,46', '0'),
(98, 197, 'Tomb Traps', 'Zhoom as given you the location to this tomb hidden in the sands and lost in time.', 'You have located the treasure of the tomb, and escaped the ancient burial chamber! The Sandsea seems have a million of these hidden tombs! Maybe Zhoom knows where another one is.', 'quests/quest-traps4.swf', 'quests/quest-traps-xmap.swf', 0, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 500000, 'none', 1, 99, 'mummy and sunspike', 'mset-templetraps.swf', '220,229', '0'),
(99, 198, 'The Sandsea', '', '', 'towns/Sandsea/town-sandsea16.swf', 'none', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 98, 'Sandsea=towns/Sandsea/town-sandsea16.swf\nPalace=towns/Sandsea/town-sekduat5.swf\nInn=towns/Sandsea/Sandsea-Inn.swf\nhelmshop=towns/Sandsea/shop-SandSeahelm.swf\nAdvCrest=towns/town-falconreach-Feb12-10r2.swf \nMystery=zones/zone-mysterious.swf\nWillowshire=zon', 0, 0, 'none', 'none', '5,6,7', '0'),
(100, 199, 'Meeting Zhoom', 'The Sandsea seems to have more sub-plots than grains of sand!', 'You have lost your one contact to the resistance... and your one lead to the location of the Orb of Light. Working with Zhoom might be your only way to get back in touch with the resistance!', 'towns/Sandsea/quest-zhoom1.swf', 'none', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 500000, 'none', 0, 0, 'none', 'none', '5,6,7', '0'),
(101, 202, 'Roliths Test', 'Cause having my own town was not enough', 'WOOT.', 'towns/TheLocker/quest-kathooltest.swf', 'none', 4000, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 354, 'none', 0, 99, 'Elder god', 'mset-kathool.swf', '494', '0'),
(102, 208, 'Heart-Shaped Box', 'Big Daddy has sent you deep into the Forest of Infinite Terror to the home of the Snugvils to retrieve his Heart-Shaped Box.', 'Well, you found the box which was being jealously guarded by the Snugvils, but they had no interest in the contents. Whatever was in that box got dumped out. What could have been in a box that large?', 'towns/heroheart/quest-heartbox.swf', 'none', 0, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 39228, 'none', 1, 99, '<3', 'mset-lovesneevil.swf', '235,236,238', '0'),
(103, 215, 'The Traitor', 'Sek-Duat XV has sent you to meet with a member of the rebellion who has decided to turn traitor. You have to stop the turncoat if you can!', 'Kasuf vanishes into the desert, looking defeated and full of regret. That was a close call, but the rebellion is safe, thanks to you. Why did Sek-Duat send you instead of Zhoom? What does he have up his sleeve?', 'towns/Sandsea/quest-zhoom7r1.swf', 'none', 0, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 101703, 'none', 1, 99, 'Werewolf, Ele', 'mset-anubis.swf', '46,243', '0'),
(104, 218, 'Sek-Duat Lives Again', 'You and Zhoom are on your way to stop Sek-Duat XV from his evil plans.', 'You and Zhoom have defeated the ancient lord of all The Sandsea! The battle is won but the fight is far from over. He is still ruler of land with huge armies under his control, but you have won the day and the Orb of Light is yours!', 'towns/Sandsea/quest-zhoom9.swf ', 'none', 2000, 2000, 0, 9000, 1, 93476, 'none', 1, 99, 'eygptian', 'mset-sekduat.swf', '229,243,246', '0'),
(105, 222, 'Lymcrest', 'A friendly mining town populated by dwarven and human miners.', 'A friendly mining town populated by dwarven and human miners.', 'towns/Lymcrest/town-lymcrest9.swf', 'none', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 243, 'Lymcrest=towns/Lymcrest/town-lymcrest9.swf', 0, 0, 'none', 'none', '5,6,7', '0'),
(106, 225, 'Battle for Moonridge!', 'The town of Moonridge, deep within Doomwood, has fallen under attack from waves of the undead and sent to Falconreach for help!', 'You have cleared the streets of the invading undead, but the waves keep coming! If you can clear them all maybe you and Artix can find out the reason for the attacks.', 'wars/quest-necrowar2.swf', 'none', 0, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 20151, 'none', 1, 99, 'Darkness, Undead', 'mset-necrowar.swf', '250,133,251,252', '0'),
(107, 228, 'The Lymcrest Labyrinth', 'Dugg has explored to the second floor of the Lymcrest Labyrinth. Can you fight your way through elementals and explore the rest of the labyrinth?', 'You have defeated Sandstone and made it to the tenth level of the Lymcrest Labyrinth, which is deeper then anyone has gone in a millennium. Go tell Doug Digg of your accomplishment and make sure to visit soon to explore deeper in the cave!', 'quests/lymcrest/floor6-10r2.swf ', 'none', 0, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 35159, 'none', 1, 99, 'elementals', 'mset-lymcrestlab1r1.swf', '231,53,52,54,36,290,291,16', '0'),
(108, 229, 'Moonridge: Saved!', 'THE CLOCK SAYS: PARTY TIME!', 'Whew! That was a close one, but now the party can really start! It looks like Lady Vayle and Artix have some history, maybe you can ask him about that later. Right now, the key to the Necropolis awaits!', 'towns/DoomWood/quest-Artix2.swf', 'none', 0, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 500000, 'none', 1, 99, 'Undead', 'mset-Armadeadon.swf', '254', '0'),
(109, 230, 'Doomwood', '', '', 'towns/DoomWood/town-doomwood17.swf', 'none', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 154, 'Doomwood=towns/Doomwood/town-doomwood17.swf', 0, 0, 'none', 'none', '5,6,7', '0'),
(110, 233, 'Battle for Moonridge!', 'The town of Moonridge, deep within Doomwood has fallen under attack from waves of the undead and sent to Falconreach for help!', 'You have cleared the streets of the invading undead, but the waves keep coming! If you can clear them all maybe you and Artix can find out the reason for the attacks.', 'wars/necrowar/quest-necrowar.swf', 'none', 0, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 500000, 'none', 1, 99, 'Darkness, Undead', 'mset-necrowar.swf', '250,133,251,252', '0'),
(111, 234, 'The Necromantress', 'You find yourself face to face with the necromantress behind the Moonridge Invasion.', 'The purple-robed Necromantress may have escaped, but Moonridge has been saved from her creations. If all of those monsters came from one necromantress, imagine what an entire class of them could do! You have to find a way into the necropolis!', 'wars/necrowar/quest-necrowar-boss.swf', 'none', 0, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 500000, 'none', 1, 99, 'Darkness, Undead', 'mset-necrowar.swf', '250,133,251,252', '0'),
(112, 239, 'The Lymcrest Labyrinth', '', '', 'quests/lymcrest/floor11-15r2.swf', 'none', 0, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 19285, 'none', 1, 99, 'lizards', 'mset-lizardsr1.swf', '16,67,177,144', '0'),
(113, 240, 'The Body Shop', 'Take down the Body Shop any way you can!', 'Well done! You have defeated your very own Build-A-Beast and destroyed the Body Shop in the process! You have slowed down production of the undead army but Sepulchure is still on his way!', 'towns/DoomWood/quest-Artix5.swf', 'none', 0, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 335824, 'none', 0, 0, 'Darkness', 'mset-artix5.swf', '101,102,103,250,257,258,259,260,261', '0'),
(114, 245, 'The Guardian Dragon', 'Finally! The last Guardian skill is within your grasp!', 'You have defeated the Guardian Dragon and been granted the final Guardian Skill. You now have the ability to summon the Guardian Dragon from his home to battle evil with you!', 'quests/quest-gdragon.swf', 'none', 0, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 5136, 'none', 1, 99, 'dragon', 'mset-guardiandragon.swf', '274', '0'),
(115, 247, 'Assault on the Necropolis', 'FOR FALCONREACH!', 'That is one wave down! The front lines appear to be edging ever closer to the main building in the Necropolis but you still have a long way to go and more undead keep pouring out of the buildings! Go heal up at Ghost, the others need your help!', 'wars/quest-war-Friday13necro-2.swf', 'none', 0, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 84848, 'none', 1, 99, 'necro', 'mset-friday13necro.swf', '88,86,252,256,265', '0'),
(116, 252, 'Monkee Business', 'Clear your war through these pirate monkees for Pi Mae.', 'With all the pirate primates defeated those ninjas swept in to fling... um, mud... and vandalize the Osprey Cove Inn. Mission Accomplished!', 'quests/quest-monkeebusiness.swf', 'none', 0, 2000, 0, 9000, 0, 143998, 'none', 0, 99, 'Pirates', 'mset-pnwar-pirates.swf', '202,203,206,205,204', '0');
